02</a>"},{"pid":"562936e87f3602565cce637fdc518ac10a9bbfe9","tid":1491594,"uid":308875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T00:30:12.000Z","msg":"英國重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍<br />\n<br />\n英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n記得同父母講簽左有咩好處<br />\n點解要簽?<br />\n1.居英權 <br />\n2.去美國唔洗簽證 <br />\n3.英國係法治，非人治 <br />\n4.民主自由 <br />\n5.房屋政策教好 <br />\n6. 去歐美國家入境時唔會被問長問短 <br />\n7. 00後可以用家庭團聚形式入籍 <br />\n8.攞到脫離現有被強加國籍啲條件<br />\n9.英國無再教育營<br />\n10.無2047問題<br />\n11.因為多左英國公民喺香港，英國政府會易D發聲<br />\n12.如取消左被強加國籍，可以喺香港call領事保護及用英國護照入境中國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPostal code 填000000<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9pNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=c4d80085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"5a46f2bd0b7c0fedc31120c0b2c3b6bd5d8a4b95","tid":1491594,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:31:19.000Z","msg":"就黎60000了<br />\n快簽<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9pNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=c4d80085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n推上國會討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9656122a3938148371952e4da04322705b4071","tid":1491594,"uid":6034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3efb65205bc069082665295a302cf7813